"{\"uid\": \"uppermichiganssource.com-2024-09-10-community-torch-run-raises-money-awareness-special-olympics\", \"entities\": [{\"sentence\": \"IRON MOUNTAIN, Mich. (WLUC) - Drivers on US-2 in Iron Mountain may have noticed a group of 60 people marching south towards the Iron Mountain Police Department on Tuesday morning.\", \"from\": 0, \"to\": 179, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 22, \"end\": 26, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/WLUC-TV\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"WLUC\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/WLUC-TV\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/WLUC-TV\"}, {\"begin\": 128, \"end\": 141, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Iron_Mountain,_Michigan\", \"score\": 0.9540407522230475, \"rank\": 0.03574939672893003, \"text\": \"Iron Mountain\", \"types\": [\"Q515\", \"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Iron_Mountain,_Michigan\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Iron_Mountain,_Michigan\"}, {\"begin\": 142, \"end\": 159, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Police\", \"score\": 0.9986203025905125, \"rank\": 0.0008198078545528618, \"text\": \"Police Department\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Police\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Police\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The Iron Mountain Community Torch Run returned, raising money and awareness for the Special Olympics.\", \"from\": 181, \"to\": 282, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 185, \"end\": 198, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Iron_Mountain,_Michigan\", \"score\": 0.9540407522230475, \"rank\": 0.03574939672893003, \"text\": \"Iron Mountain\", \"types\": [\"Q515\", \"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Iron_Mountain,_Michigan\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Iron_Mountain,_Michigan\"}, {\"begin\": 265, \"end\": 281, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Special_Olympics\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 3.368115321323762e-14, \"text\": \"Special Olympics\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Special_Olympics\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Special_Olympics\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The group of Special Olympics athletes, organizers and parents was led by torch bearer and IMPD Deputy Director Adam Ray.\", \"from\": 284, \"to\": 405, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 297, \"end\": 313, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Special_Olympics\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 3.368115321323762e-14, \"text\": \"Special Olympics\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Special_Olympics\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Special_Olympics\"}, {\"begin\": 375, \"end\": 379, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Indianapolis_Metropolitan_Police_Department\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"IMPD\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Indianapolis_Metropolitan_Police_Department\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Indianapolis_Metropolitan_Police_Department\"}, {\"begin\": 396, \"end\": 404, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Adam_Ray_(comedian)\", \"score\": 0.9999930423876894, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Adam Ray\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Adam_Ray_(comedian)\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Adam_Ray_(comedian)\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"To be able to give back to the Special Olympics community is just amazing,\\\" Ray said.\", \"from\": 407, \"to\": 493, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"To see the expression and appreciation on the athletes faces to be able to compete in the events is pretty awesome.\\\"\", \"from\": 494, \"to\": 611, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Michigan State Police Trooper Geno Basanese brought up the rear of the walkers.\", \"from\": 613, \"to\": 692, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 613, \"end\": 621, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Michigan\", \"score\": 0.959647656853364, \"rank\": 0.04203941185483386, \"text\": \"Michigan\", \"types\": [\"Q3455524\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Michigan\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Michigan\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"He's joined the community torch run since it was revived in 2014.\", \"from\": 693, \"to\": 758, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"He says there is plenty of support from people around Dickinson County.\", \"from\": 760, \"to\": 831, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 814, \"end\": 830, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Dickinson_County,_Kansas\", \"score\": 0.5706126998523634, \"rank\": 0.3895954962468137, \"text\": \"Dickinson County\", \"types\": [\"Q3455524\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Dickinson_County,_Kansas\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Dickinson_County,_Kansas\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"It just shows, for how long we have been doing it, is the community support,\\\" Basanese said.\", \"from\": 833, \"to\": 926, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"And it's been great, because at the end of the day, it's for the athletes, they do amazing.\", \"from\": 927, \"to\": 1019, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"It's just the monetary assistance really helps.\\\"\", \"from\": 1020, \"to\": 1068, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Dickinson-Iron Intermediate School District Special Education Supervisor Lisa Anderson brought students from the ISD to walk.\", \"from\": 1070, \"to\": 1195, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1114, \"end\": 1131, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Special_education\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 4.224689623237264e-23, \"text\": \"Special Education\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Special_education\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Special_education\"}, {\"begin\": 1143, \"end\": 1156, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Lisa_Anderson\", \"score\": 0.9999999999997726, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Lisa Anderson\", \"types\": [\"Q82955\", \"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Lisa_Anderson\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Lisa_Anderson\"}, {\"begin\": 1183, \"end\": 1186, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Independent_school_district\", \"score\": 0.9999991234912362, \"rank\": 6.788107733924625e-07, \"text\": \"ISD\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Independent_school_district\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Independent_school_district\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"She says the students appreciate being a part of the torch run.\", \"from\": 1196, \"to\": 1259, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"So, our student's love the torch run,\\\" Anderson said.\", \"from\": 1261, \"to\": 1315, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1301, \"end\": 1309, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Chase_Anderson\", \"score\": 0.9603164382318145, \"rank\": 0.04131979850956004, \"text\": \"Anderson\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\", \"Q10871364\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Chase_Anderson\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Chase_Anderson\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"They love racing against each other, they love participating with the law enforcement officers, and they just love getting out and being together.\\\"\", \"from\": 1316, \"to\": 1464, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"The walk raised almost $1,430 for the Special Olympics.\", \"from\": 1466, \"to\": 1521, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1504, \"end\": 1520, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Special_Olympics\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 3.368115321323762e-14, \"text\": \"Special Olympics\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Special_Olympics\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Special_Olympics\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"To find resources to donate online, go to theTorch Run website.\", \"from\": 1523, \"to\": 1586, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Copyright 2024 WLUC.\", \"from\": 1588, \"to\": 1608, \"entities\": []}, {\